  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA44">
<l>ciṟantārk keḻutuṇaiyāñ ceṅkaṇmā ṉāma</l>
<l>maṟantārai māṉiṭamā vaiyē – ṉaṟantāṅku</l>
<l>mātavaṉē yeṉṉu maṉampaṭaittu maṟṟavaṉpē</l>
<l>rōtuvatē nāviṉā luḷḷu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The names of red-eyed Māl are the high[est] aid to the best people.</l>
<l>I don’t hold with those who, being human, have forgotten [them].</l>
<l>Having created a mind that says, ‘o Mātavaṉ who upholds the Dharma’</l>
<l>remember moreover to recite his names with the tongue.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
